    <item>
      <title>《猜疑链 vs 师生共生》—— 从三体看硅基文明的未来</title>
      <link>https://mingjian.cc/zh/posts/2026-04-02-suspicion-chain-vs-teacher-symbiosis/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
